data.title: Comprehensive Silver Full Body Checkup
data.discription: Unhealthy lifestyle and stress can gradually take a toll on our health. Early detection can help to capture the warning signs of masked diseases in the body. Comprehensive Silver Full Body Checkup Package provides a comprehensive range of tests that check your liver & kidney function, blood sugar, thyroid status, lipid profile, blood profile, vitamins, minerals, urine and more.Overall, the package includes all the goodness of Good Health Platinum Package with the addition of Vitamin B12, iron tests and calcium. This package – a part of our ‘premium range’ of diagnostic tests – can be ordered once every 6 to 12 months or as recommended by your doctor.
